cf.lukasheinzl.mc.api

Class CommandRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • cf.lukasheinzl.mc.api.CommandRegistry

  • public class CommandRegistry
extends java.lang.Object
    This class can be used to manage CommandHandlers. The handleCommand method can be called in the JavaPlugin.onCommand method to handle all registered commands.
    Author:
    Lukas Heinzl

      • handleCommand

        public static boolean handleCommand(org.bukkit.command.CommandSender sender,
                                    org.bukkit.command.Command cmd,
                                    java.lang.String commandLabel,
                                    java.lang.String[] args)

        cmd - The issued command
